&gt; and Molly apparently uses the AK? And after we told that its wrong to
&gt; fight evil with evil, remember Crouch? What do u all think?
">

As far as I could make out, Molly doesn't seemed to have used the Killing
curse.

Your argument is a contentious one. Someone must ask this question to
Rowling when she next consents for an interview.
