The point is that the Ministry of Magic is a terribly flawed
organization.  JKR showed us that time and time again.  The wrongful
imprisonment of Stan Shunpike et.al, so they'd look srong in the fight
against LV. The fact that they forced the Daily Prophet to not print
anything important. Hiding mass breakouts.  Tracing young wizards so
